com.ephesoft.gxt.systemconfig.client

Interface SystemConfigService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DCMARemoteService, com.google.gwt.user.client.rpc.RemoteService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SystemConfigServiceImpl

    @RemoteServiceRelativePath(value="systemConfigService")
public interface SystemConfigService
extends DCMARemoteService
    Service class to import/export regex pool, import/export table column pool, get list of regex groups and table column pool, get license details.
